ğŸš§ Limitations & Open Questions

FC-496 implements a non-neutral bit architecture in which all bits contribute to global structural coherence.
Any unauthorized modification introduces inconsistencies that prevent the cell from satisfying its error-correction and indexing constraints, resulting in either automatic correction or structural invalidation.

